{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wordlike is a word roguelike\u2014make words, tune your bag of letters, and collect power-ups to beat increasingly difficult levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you've played Balatro, it's like Balatro with words \ud83d\udd20</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A word-based deckbuilder\u00a0</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beat each\u00a0round by constructing words, and\u00a0tune your bag of letters to optimize your draws.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/main.gif?t=1729283724\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Powerful 'Knick Knacks'\u00a0</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy Knick Knacks\u00a0to boost your score,\u00a0enhance letters, and tune your bag.\u00a0Discover unique word-based synergies based on parts of speech, letters, slang, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/choose.gif?t=1729283724\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Face challenging bosses\u00a0</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Encounter a variety of bosses that challenge you to make words without consonants, avoid nouns, or make words you've never made before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/boss.gif?t=1729283724\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unique runs every time</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each play through brings you a different bag of letters, unique bosses, and different sets of items that you can put together to make a strong build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142780/extras/board.gif?t=1729283724\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><